<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-28-0286 </DOCNO><TEXT>The invention involves a method of reducing environmental emissions ofcontaminants by refuse incineration, e.g. in district heating plants.The flue gases are cooled and condensed, the condensates then being neutralizedand purified. The remaining condensate is thereafter disposed of in awaste system or the like. (G.B.).</TEXT></DOC>